headline: The J.M. Smucker Co. to Present at the 2026 Consumer Analyst Group of New York (CAGNY) Conference and Sets Date to Report Third Quarter Earnings
summary: The J.M. Smucker Co. (NYSE: SJM) invites interested parties to listen to management's presentation during the 2026 CAGNY Conference on Wednesday, Feb. 18, 2026, at 2:00 p.m. Eastern Standard Time.
